com.joliciel.talismane.tokeniser.features

Class TokenFeatureParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.joliciel.talismane.tokeniser.features.TokenFeatureParser

  • public class TokenFeatureParser
extends java.lang.Object
    A helper class for adding generic token features to any parser requiring them. See addFeatureClasses(FeatureClassContainer).
    Author:
    Assaf Urieli
